Package: antbox
Version: 1.0.0
Section: media
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd
Recommends: linux-headers
Maintainer: Flock <support@yourflock.org>
Description: AntBox - USB tuner live TV daemon for Owl
 AntBox turns any Linux machine with a USB DVB TV tuner into a live TV
 source for Owl. It discovers tuner hardware, captures MPEG-TS streams,
 and streams them to an Owl backend via gRPC.
